Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.74,0:01:19.70,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(167,167)}問いかけたまま
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.99,0:01:25.87,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(167,167)}答えはもう届かなかった
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.83,0:01:34.09,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(167,167)}溢れた感情を失くさないで
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.13,0:01:40.14,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(167,167)}心があれば守り抜けるさ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.14,0:01:46.23,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(167,167)}命の音が聞こえるだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.23,0:01:52.23,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(167,167)}心の中 きみがいるから
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.23,0:01:54.53,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(167,167)}We will remember your name
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.53,0:01:56.82,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(167,167)}We will remember your dream
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.82,0:01:58.45,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(167,167)}Remember you're braver
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.45,0:02:00.62,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(167,167)}We will remember your name
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.62,0:02:02.95,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(167,167)}We will remember your dream
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.95,0:02:05.08,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(167,167)}Remember you're braver
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.37,0:02:10.50,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(167,167)}朱く焼けた世界を闇が青に染めて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.50,0:02:12.50,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(167,167)}この目で見た
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.50,0:02:14.88,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(167,167)}その目に焼き付いた
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.05,0:02:17.22,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(167,167)}Remember you're braver
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.38,0:02:20.01,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(167,167)}遥かなる道を
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.30,0:02:23.47,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(167,167)}積み重なる悲しみを
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.64,0:02:27.44,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(167,167)}きみと生きよう
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.48,0:02:32.27,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(167,167)}僅かな望みを
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.52,0:02:35.53,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(167,167)}答えのないその問いを
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.53,0:02:37.15,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(167,167)}もう一度
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.28,0:02:41.16,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(167,167)}もう二度と
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.74,0:01:19.70,OPCNcht,,0,0,0,,{\fad(167,167)}叩問內心
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.99,0:01:25.87,OPCNcht,,0,0,0,,{\fad(167,167)}終究沒有得到答案
